CREATE TABLE customersetup.accounts (
    id varchar(50) NOT NULL, --account id,
    customerid varchar(50), -- customer id from customersetup.customers,
    businessunitid varchar(50), -- business unit id from customersetup.businessunits,
    businessunitnumber varchar(50), -- business unit number from customersetup.businessunits,
    accountcode varchar(15) NOT NULL, -- account code, 
    description varchar(50), -- account description,
    currency varchar(50) NOT NULL, -- currency code,
    currencyid varchar(50), -- currency id from customersetup.currencies,
    metrics varchar(50), -- metrics code,
    metricsid varchar(50), -- metrics id,
    isactive bpchar NOT NULL, -- active status of a account,
    activedate timestamp NOT NULL, -- active date of a account,
    inactivedate timestamp -- inactive date of a account,
    isaggregate bpchar -- aggregate status of a account,
    createdby varchar(250)  -- created by user,
    createddate timestamp -- created date of account,
    modifiedby varchar(250) -- modified by user,
    modifieddate timestamp -- modified date of account,
    timeinepoch numeric -- time in epoch format,
    isdeleted bpchar -- deleted status of a account,
    isarchived bpchar -- archived status of a account,
    synapsefacilityname varchar(40) -- synapse facility name,
    environmentcode varchar(40) -- environment code,
    isverticaldefault bpchar -- vertical default status of a account,
    currentappversion varchar(7) -- current app version of customersetup,
    modifiedappversion varchar(7) -- modified app version of customersetup,
    createdlocation varchar(200) -- created location of account,
    updatedlocation varchar(200) -- updated location of account,
    returnaddressline1 varchar(200) -- return address line 1,
    returnaddressline2 varchar(200) -- return address line 2,
    returnaddressline3 varchar(200) -- return address line 3,
    returncity varchar(150) -- return city,
    returnstatecode varchar(150) -- return state code,
    returnpostalcode varchar(15) -- return postal code,
    returncountrycode varchar(2) -- return country code,
    allowreturns bpchar -- allow returns status of a account,   
    allowexchange bpchar -- allow exchange status of a account,
    disposition bpchar -- disposition status of a account,
    synapsecustomerid varchar(40) -- synapse customer id,
    enableprescript bpchar -- enable pre-script status of a account,
    enablepostscript bpchar -- enable post-script status of a account,
    isadvanced bpchar -- advanced status of a account,
    numberofshift numeric -- number of shifts for a account,
    lineofbusiness varchar(50) -- line of business for a account,
    accountid varchar(40) -- account id from customersetup.accounts,
    emergencycontractnumber varchar(25)  -- emergency contract number for a account,
    emergencydomesticcontact varchar(25)    -- emergency domestic contact for a account,
    emergencyintlcontact varchar(25)    -- emergency international contact for a account,
    returncontactname varchar(100)  -- return contact name for a account,
    returnwindow int4   -- return window for a account,
	CONSTRAINT accounts_id PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
